qas.question: What are some of the territories within Pakistan?

answers.text: FATA, Azad Kashmir, Northern Areas and Islamabad Capital Territory (ICT)

qas.question: What type of cases may Pakistan's Supreme Court hear from FATA?

answers.text: appeals only of a constitutional nature
